title: Demi Lovato Drops 'Waitin For You' Music Video After Press Conference in Brazil
text: Demi Lovato gets the biggest grin on her face during a press conference in Sao Paulo, Brazil earlier this week. The 23-year-old musician was awarded a Diamond Certificate after selling 160.000 copies of previous album, Demi, in just a few months!
